{"name":"WF-07-AGENT-EXECUTOR-V2","nodes":[{"parameters":{"content":"## WF-07 вЂ” Agent Executor V2\n**ExГ©rcito Comercial de IA вЂ” Motor Principal**\n\nValores reais preenchidos вЂ” pronto para importar e testar.\n\n**TESTE MANUAL (apГіs importar):**\nPOST https://n8n.julianosalles.com.br/webhook-test/agent-executor\n```json\n{\n  \"conversation_id\": \"483ff60f-909d-471e-ab53-109f916ad389\",\n  \"lead_id\": \"bcd4c7d6-a349-4e6b-8b48-0fd7023802fb\",\n  \"agent_id\": \"809664ac-d7cb-4280-a573-f251cca9d100\",\n  \"company_id\": \"32a1ab33-e2f2-4c33-b6b4-5a4d00e7e2ed\",\n  \"input_text\": \"OlГЎ, tenho interesse no produto\",\n  \"content_type\": \"text\"\n}\n```\n\n**IMPORTANTE:** O prompt Г© lido DINAMICAMENTE de ai_agents.opening_script.\nEdite em NextSales в†’ Agentes IA в†’ Editar Agente.","height":320,"width":500,"color":4},"id":"f0e1d2c3-b4a5-9687-8079-6a5b4c3d2e1f","name":"Sticky Note - InstruГ§ГЈo","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[0,-200]},{"parameters":{"httpMethod":"POST","path":"agent-executor","responseMode":"responseNode","options":{}},"id":"a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234560001","name":"Webhook","type":"n8n-nodes-base.webhook","typeVersion":2,"position":[0,300],"webhookId":"agent-executor"},{"parameters":{"respondWith":"text","responseBody":"ok","options":{}},"id":"a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234560002","name":"Respond 200 OK","type":"n8n-nodes-base.respondToWebhook","typeVersion":1,"position":[280,140]},{"parameters":{"url":"https://fhkhamwrfwtacwydukvb.supabase.co/rest/v1/ai_agents","sendQuery":true,"queryParameters":{"parameters":[{"name":"id","value":"=eq.{{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.agent_id }}"},{"name":"select","value":"*"}]},"sendHeaders":true,"headerParameters":{"parameters":[{"name":"apikey","value":"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpc3MiOiJzdXBhYmFzZSIsInJlZiI6ImZoa2hhbXdyZnd0YWN3eWR1a3ZiIiwicm9sZSI6InNlcnZpY2Vfcm9sZSIsImlhdCI6MTc2NTMyNjcxMywiZXhwIjoyMDgwOTAyNzEzfQ.slNbow0lzBpryTaPPNNPDOV5x_uBqRHQZR38RRk9